  override val startShort =
    "As the gentle sea breeze whispers through the blossoming wisteria and olive groves of Cinque Terre, Italy, there's an unspoken promise of beauty and calmness in the air. The pastel-colored villages cascade down rugged cliffs like watercolors brought to life, while a leisurely boat awaits to carry us upon the deep blue embrace of the Ligurian Sea." /
    "With the fresh zest of citrus lingering from the local groves and the easy rhythm of lapping waves, we prepare to embark on a sightseeing tour that is the epitome of springtime magnificence. It's an idyllic setting where the timeless allure of Italy converges with the simplicity of coastal life, ready to unfold its secrets to us as we glide forward, easing into the embrace of this enchanting Italian Riviera." /
    "Our first stop is the welcoming shores of Monterosso al Mare Beach, a jewel nestled within Cinque Terre. As we step onto the extensive strip of golden sand, the largest across Cinque Terre's quintet of villages, we settle into the knowledge that the day ahead is ours to savor." /
    "The sun warms our skin and the mild brine of the sea tickles our senses. With a reputation crowned by the Blue Flag status, the waters here are as clear as glass, inviting us to dip our toes into the embrace of the Mediterranean." /
    "To our side stands the impressive statue of Neptune, a striking sentinel sculpted from the stone by the hands of Arrigo Minerbi in the early twentieth century. Its massive form is a marker of creative endeavor, commanding attention against the backdrop of blue skies and the sea's endless canvas." /
    "Behind us, the historical heart of Monterosso whispers tales from the Middle Ages, its narrow streets and hidden squares untouched by the rush of the modern world. The air carries a quiet hum, a blending of waves and wind that feels like a lullaby for the soul." /
    "As we stroll by the waterfront, we see visitors lounging underneath brightly colored umbrellas, their day's agenda spelled out in shades of relaxation and quiet. Some drift towards the sea in paddle boats, casting long shadows on the sun-kissed surface, creating patterns that dance alongside the rhythm of their explorations." /
    "A walk along the shoreline offers the simplest pleasure—a melody of sensations as the sand slips between our toes, quiet conversations with passersby who share our quest for calm, and the gentle soundtrack of the Ligurian Sea softly applauding our presence. Here, in Monterosso, we surrender to the unhurried pace of Italian coastal living, allowing the springtime to unfold its wonders around us."

  override val middleShort = listOf(
    "After soaking in the sun and the calming atmosphere of Monterosso al Mare Beach, we make our way to the renowned Via dell'Amore. A gentle boat ride ushers us to the start of this coastal wonder, part of the enchanting Cinque Terre National Park—a patchwork of nature's finest work, proudly holding its title as a UNESCO World Heritage Site." /
    "This pathway, known affectionately as the 'Way of Love,' unfolds before us like a love letter composed by the landscape itself, its sentences a melodic blend of natural splendor and the whispers of those who stroll its length." /
