    "Having seized the harmonious blend of sea and village from Manarola's scenic harbor, our adventure takes a charming turn as we come across the garden of Nessun Dorma Cinque Terre. Situated in the lively clasp of Manarola, this establishment resonates softly with the melody of its namesake aria, 'Nessun Dorma,' extracted from the renowned opera 'Turandot' by Giacomo Puccini." /
