    "With hearts light and appetites satisfied, we continue to the noble remnant of Cinque Terre's storied past: Vernazza's Doria Castle. A steady ascent up the well-worn stone steps, each one warmed by the sun and seasoned by centuries of travelers, takes us back to an era where these lands were filled with stories of daring and defense." /
