    "At the core of the fortress, casually resting against its ancient walls, we are joined in a quiet togetherness—a shared instance of wonder at the magnificence that history and nature have woven together.",

    "Descending from the heights of Doria Castle, we find ourselves drawn to the spiritual heart of Vernazza, Santa Margherita di Antiochia Church. Sitting near the water's edge like a storied beacon, the church's impressive bell tower soars high, doubling as a steadfast watchtower from an era when pirates roamed the Mediterranean." /
