    "Leaving the lapping waves of Vernazza behind, we ascend towards the unique village of Corniglia. Poised one hundred meters above sea level, this hilltop hamlet offers stunning panoramic views that sweep across the other Cinque Terre villages towards the distant embrace of the Mediterranean." /
