    "From the high vantage point of Corniglia's terraces, where sweeping vistas hold our gaze, a narrow footpath beckons us towards an enchanting coastal secret, Guvano Beach. Known for its quiet seclusion and crystal-clear waters, Guvano remains a treasure shielded by the embrace of nature." /
