    "From the lofty terraces of Corniglia, we embark on an intimate journey to one of the region's best-kept secrets, Guvano Beach. This secluded stretch of shore captures the imagination with its history as an unofficial nudist retreat, particularly in the freewheeling days of the seventies and eighties." /
